This is a long one so bear with me ...

Today my 8 year anniversary of moving to LA from Chicago but its also the anniversary of one of the biggest things IVE EVER DONE IN MY CAREER. I will keep screaming this, I dont care overall how the film received people are entitled to feel the way they do. But i was blessed to work with people I'd been a fan of since i was a child. I had the opportunity to be directed by the legendary @officialspikelee. Watching that man at work and being part of that work was surreal. To then work alongside the legendary @realwesleysnipes who STILL NEEDS to tell jokes on stage (my goal is to get him on a stage). The homey @nickcannon whos work ethic is BANANAS, THE ICONIC @samuelljackson & @im.angelabassett to clown & bond with Kevin Wilmott @lala @thestressreliever @michellemitchenor @ronejae @ldoradojonez @bmoresnoop @whatsanyamind @theonlysteveharris @miss_poundcakes (MISS YOU ERICA)
 @coreymakesmovies @johncusack @wadeforrestwilson plus so many more FOREVER resonates with me. I'm blessed to know you all, work with you and still stay in touch with you all. Heres to MUCH MORE SUCCESS, HAPPINESS & PROSPERITY to you all.

There were times I wouldn't make it past 3 years here but now 8 in and just working my ass off day in and day out. Let's see if we can make it 8 more.
 #anniversary #ChiraqTheMovie #ASpikeLeeJoint

To record the first #AreYouStillListening for @netflixisajoke radio for the year was a validation of the work I've been putting in and to share the stage with so many dope people I rock with regularly made it even more special.
